quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,"We have indeed bestowed it [the Qur'aan] in the night of Divine Decree"
  97,2,And what do you understand what the night of divine Decree is
  97,3,The night of divine Decree is better than a thousand months
  97,4,"The angels and the Spirit, by their Lord's leave, descend in that night with all His decrees"
  97,5,"Peace it is, until the break of dawn"